author: Unreal Engine
description:
Watch this session recorded at Unreal Fest Orlando 2025 for a high-level, end-to-end overview of the systems and improvements available in UE 5.6 to reduce project iteration times, cooking assets, and testing your game through new on-target iteration workflows.

You'll come away with a deeper knowledge of what you can leverage in Unreal Engine 5.6 to improve your development strategy, including best practices for setting up and structuring projects and assets, and choosing the right settings to improve the iteration loop on your target platform.

Learn more about Unreal Engine 5.6 here: unrealengine.com/news/unreal-engine-5-6-is-now-available

#UE5.6, #GameDevelopment, #OnTargetIteration, #UnrealEngine, #UE5, #UnrealFestOrlando
title: Developer Efficiency in Unreal Engine 5.6 | Unreal Fest Orlando 2025
